<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٠٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عن جابر ابن زيد قال:</span> إذا <span class="c2">(شهدت)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> الشهود فمن يوم مات: يعني <span class="c2">(في)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> العدة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
